pl.edu.mimuw.changeanalyzer.models

Class DataSetProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.edu.mimuw.changeanalyzer.models.DataSetProvider
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReadOnlyDataSetProvider, StandardDataSetProvider

    public class DataSetProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    DataSetProvider is a top-level class reponsible for retrieving data sets either by extracting them from reposiitories or by reading files with previously extracted data. It wraps functionalities provided by a DataSetBuilder and a DataSetProcessor.
    Author:
    Adam Wierzbicki
